# SafeWork Git Rules - Basedir 허용 파일 정책
#
# ALLOWED FILES IN BASEDIR:
# - .git/ (Git 저장소)
# - .github/ (GitHub Actions)
# - .serena/ (Serena MCP)
# - docker-compose.yml (컨테이너 오케스트레이션)
# - CLAUDE.md (개발 가이드 - 로컬 전용)
# - README.md (프로젝트 문서)
#
# ALL OTHER FILES/FOLDERS ARE IGNORED

# Ignore all files and folders by default
*

# ALLOWED: Essential dot directories
!.git/
!.github/
!.serena/

# ALLOWED: Core project files
!docker-compose.yml
!README.md

# IGNORED: Development guide (local only)
CLAUDE.md

# IGNORED: All other directories and files
app/
postgres/
redis/
config/
scripts/
docs/
infrastructure/
tools/
src/
deployment/
assets/
feedback/

# IGNORED: All other files
*.md
*.yml
*.yaml
*.json
*.env
*.txt
*.py
*.js
*.html
*.css
*.sql
*.sh
*.conf
*.ini
*.cfg
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup